{"slug":"fusion-power-plant-simulator","title":"Fusion Power Plant Simulator","content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.fusionenergybase.com/fusion-power-plant-simulator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">🔗 Read original article</a></p>\n<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div>\n  <div>\n    <div>\n      <h2>Controls</h2>\n      <div>\n        <p><span id=\"heat-label\"><span data-color=\"heating\"></span>Heating energy per pulse</span><span id=\"v-heat\">50 MJ</span></p>\n        \n        <div id=\"power-ctrls\">\n              <p><span>Pulse rate</span><span id=\"v-rate\">1.00 Hz</span></p>\n              </div>\n      </div>\n      <div>\n        <p><span><span></span><span id=\"q-label-text\">Scientific gain (<span>Q</span><sub>sci</sub>)</span></span><span id=\"v-q\">10</span></p>\n        </div>\n      \n      <div id=\"simple-eff\">\n          <p><span><span data-color=\"electric\"></span>Conversion to electricity eff.</span><span id=\"v-eff\">33%</span></p>\n          </div>\n      <div>\n        <p><span><span data-color=\"recirc\"></span>Heating system eff.</span><span id=\"v-heff\">50%</span></p>\n        </div>\n      <div id=\"houseload-ctrl\">\n        <p><span><span data-color=\"houseLoad\"></span>House Load</span><span id=\"v-hload\">20 MW</span></p>\n        </div>\n      <h2 id=\"advanced-toggle\">Advanced</h2>\n      <div id=\"advanced-body\">\n        <div>\n          <p><label><span>Split conversion streams</span></label></p><div id=\"fuel-ctrl\">\n            <p><span>Fuel</span></p>\n            </div>\n          <div id=\"split-eff\">\n            <div>\n              <p><span><span data-color=\"neutron\"></span>Neutron conversion eff.</span><span id=\"v-neff\">40%</span></p>\n              </div>\n            <div>\n              <p><span><span data-color=\"alpha\"></span>Charged conversion eff.</span><span id=\"v-aeff\">20%</span></p>\n              </div>\n            <div>\n              <p><span><span data-color=\"heating\"></span>Heating conversion eff.</span><span id=\"v-hceff\">33%</span></p>\n              </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div id=\"blanket-ctrl\">\n          <p><span>Blanket Multiplication</span><span id=\"v-blanket\">1.00×</span></p>\n          </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <h2>Display</h2>\n      \n      \n      \n    </div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <p><label id=\"embed-q-label\"><span>Q</span> = 10</label>\n    \n  </p>\n  <p><label id=\"embed-eff-label\">Conversion to<br>electricity = 33%</label>\n    \n  </p>\n  <p><label id=\"embed-heff-label\">Heating<br>system = 50%</label>\n    \n  </p>\n  <p><label id=\"embed-heating-label\">Heating<br>power = 50 MW</label>\n    \n  </p>\n  <p><label id=\"embed-hload-label\">House = 20 MW</label>\n    \n  </p>\n  <p><label id=\"embed-rate-label\">Rate = 5.0 Hz</label>\n    \n  </p>\n  \n  \n  \n</div></DIV>","description":"Interactive diagram showing energy flows in a fusion power plant. Adjust Q, conversion efficiency, and heating system efficiency to explore how plasma gain translates to net electricity.","created_at":"2026-04-22T10:25:00.000Z","updated_at":"2026-04-22T11:06:39.986Z","tags":["hacker-news","tech"],"thumbnail":[{"url":"https://www.fusionenergybase.com/images/fusion-simulator-preview.png"}]}